source.name: Street Structures (Zipped Shapefile Format)
source.description: Structures in the right-of-way, maintained by Public Works.  Includes Barriers; Retaining Walls; Stairs; Bridges; Tunnels, Overpasses; Pedestrian Overpasses; Ramps; Trestles; Viaducts; and other types of structures.
